doctype html
html(lang='en-GB')
  head
    title FLO Blockchain: tZERO DLR Records

    link(rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
    link(rel="icon" href="favicon-v2.png")
    meta(property="og:title" content="FLO Blockchain: tZERO DLR Records")
    meta(property="og:site_name" content="FLO Blockchain")
    meta(property="og:url" content="https://floblockchain.org/tzero/")
    meta(
        property="og:description"
        content="Explore the most recent tZERO DLR records in the FLO Blockchain using this floData explorer."
    )
    meta(property="og:type" content="website")
    meta(property="og:image" content="https://floblockchain.org/FLO.png")

  body
    div(id="top" class="floblockchain-header")
      h1
        a(href="https://floblockchain.org") FLO Blockchain
    div(style="text-align:center;")
      img(src="FLO.png" alt="FLO")
      div(class="floblockchain-text top")
        h3 Recent tZERO DLR Records
        a(id="top-link" href="#whats-this") Learn More

    table(id="tbl")
      thead
        tr
          td floData
          td time
          td txid
          td block

      - var classcount=0;
      script 
        | console.log(!{JSON.stringify(data)});
      each tx in data
        tr(class=(1+classcount++)%2 ? 'bg' : '')
          td(class="floData")= tx.tx.floData
          td
            span(title=tx.tx.time)= tx.tx.timeago
          td
            a(href=("http://network.flo.cash/tx/" + tx.tx.txid) target="_blank") #{tx.tx.txid.substring(0, 6) + "..."}
          td
            a(href=("http://network.flo.cash/block/" + tx.tx.blockhash) target="_blank") #{tx.tx.blockhash.substring(0, 6) + "..."}
    div(class="floblockchain-text")
      h2(id="whats-this") About
      p These are the recent tZERO DLRs recorded in the FLO blockchain. Click on the txid or block hash to navigate to the explorer for further research and verification of individual DLR records.
      h3 tZERO DLR
      p A DLR (Digital Locate Receipt) is a digitized version of a traditional REG SHO locate. tZEROâ€™s DLR platform captures all inventory and audit trail information and stores that information permanently on the blockchain.
      p Learn more about the tZERO DLR system here: [#[a(href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VjM-m8IZrT0") YouTube]]
      h3 How was it made?
      p This page was created using #[a(href="https://github.com/oipwg/js-oip") js-oip], a nodejs library that allows you to interact with the Open Index Protocol and the FLO blockchain. The js-oip package is also available on #[a(href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/js-oip") npm].
      p [#[a(href="#top") Back to top]]
